---
title: Butterflied Mexican Chicken with Homemade Refried Beans
description: In this flavoursome Mexican recipe, you'll learn how to butterfly chicken. It's a great time-saving technique as it means themeat cooks more quickly. Anything that speeds up dinner's arrival on the table is a good thing, right? ¡Ándale, Ándale!
